                <h3 className="text-4xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tight">Active Recall Challenge</h3>
                <p className="text-xl text-gray-500 mb-12 font-medium leading-relaxed">Our AI has mapped the core concepts of this document. Are you ready to validate your understanding with a smart assessment?</p>
                <button 
                  onClick={generateQuiz} 
